Why Does This Work?

At every step:

A rotated sorted array always has one sorted half.

Example

4 5 6 7 | 0 1 2

Left half is sorted.

or

6 7 | 0 1 2 3

Right half is sorted.

Use this property to eliminate half the array every iteration.

